subject: Super Bowl
Football
Colleges and Universities
lead_paragraph: The 49ers’ Tramaine Brock is the first student from Belhaven University, a liberal arts school in Jackson, Miss. with about 2,600 on-campus students, ever to play in the N.F.L.
